      <title>【Thinking Elixir 266: Phoenix 1.8.0 Brings Fresh Features】Thinking Elixir 266: Phoenix 1.8.0 Brings Fresh Features</title>
      <link>https://elixirstatus.com/p/u3eY5-thinking-elixir-266-phoenix-180-brings-fresh-features</link>
      <description>【&#xA;          &lt;table width=&#34;100%&#34; border=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td width=80 valign=top&gt;&#xA;                &lt;img src=&#34;https://elixirstatus.com/rss/avatar/brainlid?uid=u3eY5&#34; width=&#34;64&#34; height=&#34;64&#34; /&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td&gt;&#xA;                &lt;h1&gt;Thinking Elixir 266: Phoenix 1.8.0 Brings Fresh Features&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    19 Aug 2025&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    by&#xA;                    &lt;i class=&#34;icon-git_circle&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; brainlid&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    &#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;p&gt;&#xA;Episode 266 of &lt;a href=&#34;https://podcast.thinkingelixir.com&#34;&gt;Thinking Elixir&lt;/a&gt;. News includes the official release of Phoenix 1.8.0 with exciting new features like dark mode themes, streamlined generators, magic links in phx.gen.auth, and AGENTS.md for LLM-assisted development. ElixirLS v0.29.2 with call hierarchy provider and MCP server integration, the new Torus library for seamless PostgreSQL search with Ecto, ThinkingElixir courses becoming completely free and open, a new Elixir Hub website centralizing community resources, LiveTable v0.3.1 updates for dynamic LiveView tables, and more!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7wnz1tbTnvA&#34;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7wnz1tbTnvA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;hr&gt;&#xA;                &lt;small&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://elixirstatus.com/p/u3eY5-thinking-elixir-266-phoenix-180-brings-fresh-features&#34;&gt;View on ElixirStatus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;        】&#xA;          &lt;table width=&#34;100%&#34; border=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td width=80 valign=top&gt;&#xA;                &lt;img src=&#34;https://elixirstatus.com/rss/avatar/brainlid?uid=u3eY5&#34; width=&#34;64&#34; height=&#34;64&#34; /&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td&gt;&#xA;                &lt;h1&gt;Thinking Elixir 266: Phoenix 1.8.0 Brings Fresh Features&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    19 Aug 2025&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    by&#xA;                    &lt;i class=&#34;icon-git_circle&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; brainlid&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    &#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;p&gt;&#xA;Episode 266 of &lt;a href=&#34;https://podcast.thinkingelixir.com&#34;&gt;Thinking Elixir&lt;/a&gt;. News includes the official release of Phoenix 1.8.0 with exciting new features like dark mode themes, streamlined generators, magic links in phx.gen.auth, and AGENTS.md for LLM-assisted development. ElixirLS v0.29.2 with call hierarchy provider and MCP server integration, the new Torus library for seamless PostgreSQL search with Ecto, ThinkingElixir courses becoming completely free and open, a new Elixir Hub website centralizing community resources, LiveTable v0.3.1 updates for dynamic LiveView tables, and more!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7wnz1tbTnvA&#34;&gt;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7wnz1tbTnvA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;hr&gt;&#xA;       